name: Corneo's POV Bound Wrists Missionary Embedding
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding to generate point-of-view missionary sex positions with the wrists bound and usually above the head. Use corneo_bound_missionary to activate the embedding.

This was trained on NAI and will require a model at least partially mixed with one trained on Danbooru tagging.

Example images produced with my 7th Heaven mix available here https://civitai.com/models/4669/corneos-7th-heaven-mix and the Anything v3 VAE (no hypernetwork was used).

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!
